Origin and authorship
---------------------

Sandeep Markondiah Jayaprakash (https://github.com/sandeep-jay) was the
sole implementation author of the upstream "Chabot" codebase
(https://github.com/ets-berkeley-edu/chabot) while engaged with Berkeley
Educational Technology Services. Copyright in that work is held by The
Regents of the University of California, and that codebase is distributed
under the LICENSE in this repository.

"Campus RAG Assistant" is an independent extension that Sandeep authored
outside of that engagement, extending the upstream codebase with
multicloud providers, a Vue SPA, LangGraph orchestration, streaming chat,
Alembic migrations, tox/CI, and RAGAS + LangSmith evaluation. Because it
builds on the upstream, the extension as a whole continues to be
distributed under the same UC Regents LICENSE.

